00:00:47,290 --> 00:00:53,540
The An Byeon Chaek has been approved.

3
00:00:53,540 --> 00:00:57,500
Now, the base of revolution has been established.

4
00:00:57,500 --> 00:01:05,330
Hong In Bang, in the end, your ambition has set fire to revolution.

5
00:01:05,330 --> 00:01:07,410
Episode 10

6
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:19,040
Why are you like that?

7
00:01:24,140 --> 00:01:25,840
I'm sorry.

8
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:28,580
Did something go wrong?

9
00:01:28,580 --> 00:01:29,460
Boon...

10
00:01:29,460 --> 00:01:32,440
Ah, hurry and speak up! How did it go?

11
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:36,800
The An Byeon Chaek...
(An Byeon Chaek: a strategy to stabilize the national defense of the Northeastern border)

12
00:01:38,300 --> 00:01:40,260
has been approved!

13
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:42,770
Hey, what are you doing? People are staring.

14
00:01:42,770 --> 00:01:46,390
Is that important now? When I'm this excited!

15
00:01:46,390 --> 00:01:47,710
Did it really get passed?

16
00:01:47,710 --> 00:01:51,010
Yes. Everything went well. Everything!

17
00:01:51,010 --> 00:01:53,730
The An Byeon Chaek has been approved.

18
00:01:53,730 --> 00:01:57,890
Now, the distribution of power in Gaegyeong will be greatly restructured.

19
00:01:57,890 --> 00:02:01,290
The ones who made this amazing feat possible were us. We did it!

20
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:05,920
But that was forged. What are you going to do?

21
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:10,930
Hey, it's not the time to worry but the time to celebrate victory.

22
00:02:10,930 --> 00:02:14,000
You... As a person lives life, this kind of moment doesn't come often.

23
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:17,520
If you don't enjoy this kind of moment, you'll live a depressing life.

24
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:20,160
I don't want to live like that. No, I can't live like that.

25
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:23,820
Aigoo. Aigoo. Is that so?

26
00:02:23,820 --> 00:02:25,700
Well, I'm like that too.

27
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:31,800
You bastard, you back stabbed me?

28
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:36,500
Back stabbed? Who is it that planned an assassination and is now getting mad at me and putting the blame on me?

29
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:40,940
Assassination? When did I try to kill you?
(Lee In Gyeom)

30
00:02:40,940 --> 00:02:45,310
Not me, but my In-law. You sent an assassin last night!
(Gil Tae Mi)

31
00:02:45,310 --> 00:02:47,210
Assassin?

32
00:02:47,210 --> 00:02:49,670
What are you saying right now?

33
00:02:49,670 --> 00:02:51,170
Forget it.

34
00:02:51,170 --> 00:02:53,900
If it's not you, then it's probably General Choi Yeong.

35
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:57,140
No, what is this...

36
00:02:57,140 --> 00:03:01,570
You bastard. Do you know what you have done?

37
00:03:02,260 --> 00:03:06,850
Do you think that I don't want Lee Seong Gye to enter the Do Dang because I hate him?

38
00:03:06,850 --> 00:03:13,030
Did it look like I was scared of my authority being in danger if Lee Seong Gye sides with Choi Yeong?

39
00:03:13,030 --> 00:03:15,670
Well, it doesn't necessarily have to be that, right?

40
00:03:15,670 --> 00:03:18,750
What kind of place is the Northeastern region?

41
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:22,430
It's a place that can decide what will happen to Goryeo.

42
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:24,870
To the down-to-earth guy from that Northeastern region,

43
00:03:24,870 --> 00:03:29,210
you give him an autonomous region and if he advances to the center,

44
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:35,600
that man's strength will finally be out of our control, you stupid bastard!

45
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:40,430
If it was that important, then you shouldn't have sent an assassin.

46
00:03:40,430 --> 00:03:43,950
I said that I never sent one!

47
00:03:44,950 --> 00:03:46,700
General!

48
00:03:48,230 --> 00:03:52,820
You knew about it, right, General? What exactly happened?
(Po Eun: Jeong Mong Joo)

49
00:03:52,820 --> 00:03:55,780
I voted in favor of the An Byeon Chaek so that it gets approved.
[Choi Yeong]

50
00:03:55,780 --> 00:03:57,120
Wasn't it the same for you?

51
00:03:57,120 --> 00:04:00,140
That wasn't the case though. How is it that those people

52
00:04:00,140 --> 00:04:03,370
You can ask them that then. Why are you asking me?

53
00:04:05,550 --> 00:04:08,330
Are you going to release Hong In Bang's servants?

54
00:04:08,330 --> 00:04:12,490
Are you going to cover up what happened in the Western district?

55
00:04:12,490 --> 00:04:16,930
For a strategy to work, it needs to follow a sequence.

56
00:04:16,930 --> 00:04:18,520
I just followed the sequence.

57
00:04:18,520 --> 00:04:21,590
Then what are you going to do after that?

58
00:04:21,590 --> 00:04:24,490
He'll probably strike me afterwards.

59
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:43,830
That is not a strange thing. Isn't General Choi Yeong originally the best person for defense?
(Hong In Bang)

60
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:47,530
The thing I'm curious about isn't General Choi Yeong's thoughts

61
00:04:47,530 --> 00:04:50,310
but yours.

62
00:04:50,310 --> 00:04:53,770
Instead of offering your assets, you chose to get the An Byeon Chaek approved.

63
00:04:53,770 --> 00:04:57,650
Your hidden agenda, that's what I'm curious of.

64
00:04:58,610 --> 00:05:03,210
Could it be that you are thinking of getting General Lee Seong Gye on your side?

65
00:05:03,210 --> 00:05:06,710
Are you thinking of that?

66
00:05:06,710 --> 00:05:08,950
Just watch.

67
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:17,320
It's Bu Jeon Swae Jeon.
(Bu Jeon Swae Jeon: "Pick up a stone, hit the stone."

68
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:20,020
The world alleviation plan has really started now.

69
00:05:20,020 --> 00:05:24,360
Hong In Bang is a stone you are holding in your hands, Elder Bon Won.

70
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:27,500
But why is your face like that?

71
00:05:27,500 --> 00:05:29,860
Who could that warrior be?

72
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:32,200
Are you talking about the person that poured down Heaven's rain on us?

73
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:35,680
It's said that you can't predict where a Pok Doo will bounce to.
(Pok Doo Bul Ga Ji: it's not possible to predict where a bean will bounce to when it's being fried.)

74
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:41,380
When the Heaven's rain falls down next time, we don't know if we will be Sima Yi or Zhuge Liang.

75
00:05:41,380 --> 00:05:44,280
Are you referring to that man as the Pok Doo?
(Pok Doo: fried bean)

76
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:46,990
In this situation that I perfectly created,

77
00:05:46,990 --> 00:05:50,670
only that suspicious warrior is not included in my calculations.

78
00:05:50,670 --> 00:05:55,530
In this moment, the most dangerous thing is an uncontrolled variable.

79
00:05:55,530 --> 00:05:58,130
I will look into it.

80
00:05:58,130 --> 00:06:00,300
You have to go to Ham Joo now.

81
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:01,620
I have to.

82
00:06:01,620 --> 00:06:06,900
Now, I have to meet Lee Seong Gye and let him know about the whole plan. It's time to discuss the system of establishing a country.

83
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:09,660
Then, should I go to the cave in Ja Nam Mountain?

84
00:06:09,660 --> 00:06:10,920
Yes.

85
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:14,580
Inside the cave, if you look through the bookshelf, there will be papers inside a wooden chest.

86
00:06:14,580 --> 00:06:17,240
Please take all of it.

87
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:21,680
You! Did you lie to me or not?

88
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:26,350
What are you saying? How would I dare do that to you?
(Cho Young, Hwa Sa Dan's Owner)

89
00:06:26,350 --> 00:06:30,200
To make Hong In Bang crawl back,

90
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:32,740
I said that I will bring in Lee Seong Gye.

91
00:06:32,740 --> 00:06:35,290
Still, that bastard brought a gift

92
00:06:35,290 --> 00:06:38,100
and even said that he will lower the taxes.

93
00:06:38,100 --> 00:06:41,710
If he was thinking of being allied with Lee Seong Gye in the first place,

94
00:06:41,710 --> 00:06:47,410
shouldn't he have used it as his advantage, when I said I was going to bring in Lee Seong Gye?

95
00:06:47,410 --> 00:06:54,690
But he didn't do that. Instead, back stabbed me at the Do Dang today.

96
00:06:54,700 --> 00:06:58,900
Also, what did the person you sent say last night?

97
00:06:58,900 --> 00:07:04,080
Gil Tae Mi and Hong In Bang decided on offering half of their assets?

98
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,830
Yes, Hap Ha.

99
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:09,390
I personally heard that.

100
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:12,090
They surely decided on doing that.

101
00:07:12,090 --> 00:07:16,260
But all of a sudden, an assassin came...

102
00:07:16,260 --> 00:07:18,670
Wait, wait...

103
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:24,580
They already decided to offer half of their assets

104
00:07:24,580 --> 00:07:27,920
and an assassin came in?

105
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:31,880
They misunderstood that I sent the assassin

106
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:35,060
and changed their mind?

107
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:42,280
This situation

108
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:49,250
was not planned by Hong In Bang.

109
00:07:51,610 --> 00:07:52,910
Yes?

110
00:07:52,910 --> 00:07:57,350
What did Gil Tae Mi say about the assassin?

111
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:04,770
When their swords met, he said this, "So what happened to Baek Yoon was your doing."

112
00:08:04,770 --> 00:08:09,970
Like this, he speculated that he was the one who killed Baek Yoon.

113
00:08:09,970 --> 00:08:15,270
In this palace, there is an influential force that I am not aware of.

114
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:20,660
There is someone controlling Hong In Bang.

115
00:08:20,660 --> 00:08:24,840
A power in Gaegyeong that neither of us know about?

116
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:29,500
It must be the person who leads that assassin.

117
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:32,100
Gather all your information.

118
00:08:32,100 --> 00:08:36,790
After the attack, Hong In Bang definitely met with someone.

119
00:08:36,790 --> 00:08:38,570
Yes, Hap Ha.

120
00:08:38,570 --> 00:08:41,350
Just who?

121
00:08:41,350 --> 00:08:43,520
Wait...

122
00:08:45,850 --> 00:08:52,290
Who will benefit the most from this happening?

123
00:08:58,100 --> 00:09:00,140
Could it be...

124
00:09:00,140 --> 00:09:06,250
Are you thinking of the same thing as me?

125
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:11,310
But it's not in Lee Seong Gye's nature to do this.

126
00:09:18,730 --> 00:09:20,900
Lee Seong Gye...

127
00:09:20,900 --> 00:09:22,010
What?

128
00:09:22,010 --> 00:09:24,970
The An Byeon Chaek has been approved at the Do Dang.

129
00:09:29,100 --> 00:09:33,350
If the An Byeon Chaek has been approved...

130
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:36,390
Teacher's Sam Bong's plan worked.

131
00:09:47,580 --> 00:09:50,900
It's not because I don't trust you, Young Master.
(Moo Hyul)

132
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:55,980
Gyo Ui Bang Gwa said that "Buk Doo 2nd rank" or something doesn't exist...

133
00:09:58,930 --> 00:10:02,160
Well, my position or my housing,

134
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:04,190
how will you provide it, if you break it down...

135
00:10:04,190 --> 00:10:07,280
How many times did I tell you that is not the important thing, Warrior-nim?

136
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:10,690
No, it's not important. Ah, I'm really hungry.

137
00:10:10,690 --> 00:10:15,370
Owner, please give me one more chicken. I'm hungry.

138
00:10:16,900 --> 00:10:20,080
It's nice to enjoy life but you should stop now.
(Boon Yi)

139
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:22,450
Tell me. What are you going to do?

140
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:32,380
Father will not be able to withdraw the An Byeon Chaek.
[Lee Bang Won]

141
00:10:32,380 --> 00:10:33,690
How did you know?

142
00:10:33,690 --> 00:10:37,000
My father is General Lee Seong Gye.

143
00:10:37,730 --> 00:10:41,310
But saying, "I wasn't able to control my own child so things became like this.

144
00:10:41,310 --> 00:10:44,850
I will cancel the An Byeon Chaek." Do you think he will do it that way?

145
00:10:45,590 --> 00:10:49,050
Then how can he govern the Ga Byeol Cho?
(Ga Byeol Cho: Lee Seong Gye's secret private army)

146
00:10:49,850 --> 00:10:54,150
He'll probably be enraged but he will just keep it in.

147
00:10:54,830 --> 00:10:59,390
Of course, I'll probably get something broken somewhere or get cut off from the family.

148
00:10:59,390 --> 00:11:01,250
That, I can handle.

149
00:11:01,250 --> 00:11:03,230
You're sure, right?

150
00:11:03,230 --> 00:11:06,370
There's no way that the An Byeon Chaek will be withdrawn, right?

151
00:11:07,230 --> 00:11:09,550
You're going to withdraw the An Byeon Chaek?

152
00:11:09,550 --> 00:11:14,490
That's it. That is the Northeastern region's standpoint that will be presented at the Do Dang.

153
00:11:14,490 --> 00:11:19,870
So you, immediately get the horse running to the Do Dang and let them know that.

154
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:23,630
What are you standing there for?

155
00:11:24,610 --> 00:11:29,770
Father, if the An Byeon Chaek gets enforced, then the people coming into the Northeastern region,
[Lee Bang Gwa]

156
00:11:29,770 --> 00:11:32,150
the families of the Ga Byeol Cho soldies who died,

157
00:11:32,150 --> 00:11:35,510
even the dying people from the places our power couldn't reach,

158
00:11:35,510 --> 00:11:37,970
we will be able to watch over them.

159
00:11:37,970 --> 00:11:41,190
Is that everything? Ho Bal Do and his Yeojin tribe,
(Ho Bal Do: Yeojin tribe's Chief)

160
00:11:41,190 --> 00:11:44,490
we can raise a military power that can push them north of Yalu River.

161
00:11:44,490 --> 00:11:45,970
More than that,

162
00:11:45,970 --> 00:11:49,770
the Goryeo you have been protecting, it will be Goryeo's defense that will stabilize.

163
00:11:49,770 --> 00:11:52,310
Are you also thinking of not listening to your father's words?

164
00:11:52,310 --> 00:11:55,430
I have the same thoughts as Bang Gwa.

165
00:11:56,490 --> 00:11:59,230
If the An Byeon Chaek is enforced,
[Lee Ji Ran]

166
00:12:00,070 --> 00:12:04,050
wouldn't you be the one who can do it best, Hyung-nim?

167
00:12:04,050 --> 00:12:11,020
Are you going to waste the Northeast's tax revenue like those stealing bastards in the Do Dang?

168
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:16,100
I will use it.

169
00:12:16,100 --> 00:12:22,520
In my entire life! For the first time, I will use them in vain.

170
00:12:22,520 --> 00:12:26,360
When I said I'm not going to go into politics, did you think it was because I didn't know what politics is?

171
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:28,570
Politics is like that.

172
00:12:28,570 --> 00:12:32,910
To get the An Byeon Chaek approved, whether it is Hong In Bang or Lee In Gyeom,

173
00:12:32,910 --> 00:12:34,890
we got help from one of them.

174
00:12:34,890 --> 00:12:40,270
Then, it becomes a situation where I joined hands with those people.

175
00:12:42,800 --> 00:12:47,770
But I, Lee Seong Gye,

176
00:12:47,770 --> 00:12:51,830
because of my son's arrogant behavior and the words of a scholar I somehow met,

177
00:12:51,830 --> 00:12:56,310
do you think I will do that? I will never do it.

178
00:12:58,900 --> 00:13:05,850
If I, Lee Seong Gye, didn't make up my mind to do something, I never act on it.

179
00:13:08,310 --> 00:13:14,590
So Bang Gwa, get a horse running to the Do Dang and let them know that.

180
00:13:14,590 --> 00:13:21,270
And Lee Shin Jeok, tell Jeong Do Jeon not to dream in vain.

181
00:13:22,250 --> 00:13:24,730
- And Young Gyu.
- Yes.

182
00:13:24,730 --> 00:13:28,760
Secretly tell Bang Woo to capture that bastard Bang Won and bring him here.

183
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:30,230
Yes.

184
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:39,130
Why did they arrest me?
[Juk Ryong: Bi Guk Temple Head Monk]

185
00:13:39,130 --> 00:13:42,610
How are things going?

186
00:13:42,610 --> 00:13:45,010
Did I get caught for nothing?

187
00:13:45,010 --> 00:13:48,550
Excuse me. What's going to happen to me?

188
00:13:48,550 --> 00:13:52,190
Look here. Hey!

189
00:14:00,850 --> 00:14:03,170
Is Monk Juk Ryong still not here?

190
00:14:03,170 --> 00:14:05,010
Yes.

191
00:14:05,010 --> 00:14:08,410
But where did you send Monk Juk Ryong?

192
00:14:08,410 --> 00:14:12,870
Things went well so he'll be back soon. Is Sam bong inside?

193
00:14:12,870 --> 00:14:15,290
He's in the Monk's room.

194
00:14:24,630 --> 00:14:28,240
The two of you didn't have a good relationship, right?

195
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:30,490
Ah, well... kind of.

196
00:14:32,300 --> 00:14:37,590
Well, how can I have a good relationship with someone?
(Sam Bong: Jeong Do Jeon)

197
00:14:37,590 --> 00:14:42,920
In-law persuaded me so I voted in favor of the An Byeon Chaek

198
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:45,130
but what are we going to do?

199
00:14:45,130 --> 00:14:47,720
I am going to leave for Ham Joo in a while.

200
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:52,790
When I get back, I will have the proof of my alliance with General Lee Seong Gye.

201
00:14:52,790 --> 00:14:55,140
I'll be expecting it.

202
00:14:55,140 --> 00:14:59,790
Then, this time, when you get back from Ham Joo,

203
00:14:59,790 --> 00:15:02,000
I'll see you in Gaegyeong.

204
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:05,910
It's an access tile to Gaegyeong.

205
00:15:05,910 --> 00:15:09,910
I cancelled the Gyeong Wi Jong Pyeon against you, Sam Bong.
(Gyeong Wi Jong Pyeon: order that prevents one who is exiled from going into Gaegyeong after release.)

206
00:15:09,910 --> 00:15:12,940
This...

207
00:15:12,940 --> 00:15:16,630
I'm a Su Shi Joong so something like this is not much.
 (Su Shi Joong: The highest ranking political figure in Goryeo - like a prime minister.)

208
00:15:16,630 --> 00:15:18,710
I'm so happy I'm almost in tears.

209
00:15:18,710 --> 00:15:20,870
I can now meet you more often.

210
00:15:20,870 --> 00:15:22,600
That's right.

211
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:26,360
But Sam Bong, when you go into Gaegyeong, you should also be careful.

212
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:31,390
If not for me, we, including In-law, will be on our way to the underworld. You know that, right?

213
00:15:31,390 --> 00:15:34,270
I was going to ask about that anyway.

214
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:36,130
Who do you think that assassin is?

215
00:15:36,130 --> 00:15:39,850
You are familiar with all the distinguished warriors out there.

216
00:15:39,850 --> 00:15:42,670
That's why it's driving me crazy too.

217
00:15:42,670 --> 00:15:45,690
There's no way that a person of that skill just suddenly appeared.

218
00:15:45,690 --> 00:15:49,040
A warrior is bound to be revealed during the process of building their skill.

219
00:15:49,040 --> 00:15:53,300
So you also don't know about it?

220
00:15:53,300 --> 00:15:55,600
It's obvious.

221
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:58,750
Don't you think that Hap Ha secretly trained him?

222
00:15:58,750 --> 00:16:05,100
The Elder is secretly having different thoughts for when he abandons me.

223
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:10,900
That assassin is not under Lee In Gyeom.

224
00:16:10,900 --> 00:16:14,600
He doesn't have any reason to do that to Hong In Bang and Gil Tae Mi.

225
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:18,120
Just who's authority is he under?

226
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:24,600
Hae Dong Gap Jok? Those people don't move for something like this.
(Hae Dong Gap Jok: a noble family of 10 generations during the Unified Silla Kingdom.)

227
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:28,280
Who exactly is giving him orders?

228
00:16:29,410 --> 00:16:31,660
Elder Bon Won!

229
00:16:33,410 --> 00:16:36,850
Regarding the Pok Doo you were talking about. That assassin.
(Pok Doo: fried bean)

230
00:16:36,850 --> 00:16:39,040
I found out who's controlling him.

231
00:16:39,040 --> 00:16:40,750
Who is it?

232
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:45,210
That... It's you, Elder Bon Won.

233
00:16:45,210 --> 00:16:47,450
What are you saying?

234
00:16:47,450 --> 00:16:51,900
Inside the cave in Ja Nam Mountain, this letter...

235
00:16:51,900 --> 00:16:56,020
Sam Bong, I killed Baek Yoon according to your Pyeong Jeong Ji Gye.
(Pyeong Jeong Ji Gye: a plan to alleviate the world)

236
00:16:56,020 --> 00:17:01,140
But this world is becoming worse.

237
00:17:02,650 --> 00:17:04,740
Who exactly is this person?

238
00:17:04,740 --> 00:17:06,850
You don't know?
(Yeon Hee)

239
00:17:06,850 --> 00:17:10,880
How can a person you don't know be mad at you?

240
00:17:10,880 --> 00:17:15,500
Also, how did he know about that place and the Pyeong Jeong Ji Gye Chaek?

241
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:19,770
I only talked about that plan to you and Hong In Bang.

242
00:17:21,690 --> 00:17:25,100
Who exactly is he?

243
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:37,800
Did you go to Ham Joo and came back?

244
00:17:37,800 --> 00:17:43,430
Hyung-nim, by any chance, did Bang Gwa Hyung or Young Gyu come here?

245
00:17:43,430 --> 00:17:46,370
They are probably in Ham Joo. Why would they be here?
(Lee Bang Woo: Lee Bang Won's older brother)

246
00:17:46,370 --> 00:17:48,970
What are you doing and not greeting him?

247
00:17:48,970 --> 00:17:50,670
Ah!

248
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:57,140
I am Young Master Bang Won's 2nd rank Buk Doo bodyguard,

249
00:17:57,140 --> 00:17:58,990
Moo Hyul.

250
00:17:58,990 --> 00:18:01,900
- Buk Doo... what?
- Bodyguard.

251
00:18:01,900 --> 00:18:05,770
I gave a position to him.

252
00:18:05,770 --> 00:18:08,800
I saved Young Master's life not once, but twice,

253
00:18:08,800 --> 00:18:11,670
I am warrior Moo Hyul.

254
00:18:11,670 --> 00:18:14,390
- Is that true.
- Yes. It is true.

255
00:18:14,390 --> 00:18:16,420
Also, this lady,

256
00:18:18,100 --> 00:18:20,750
I, twice...

257
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:25,510
Did this lady also save you?

258
00:18:26,740 --> 00:18:29,040
No.

259
00:18:29,040 --> 00:18:32,940
She bit me twice. On my arm.

260
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:41,490
It would be great if you can arrange a place for them here at the military troop in Gaegyeong.

261
00:18:41,490 --> 00:18:44,930
That person has an amazing innate strength.

262
00:18:44,930 --> 00:18:48,450
I think it will be great if you can train him under you.

263
00:18:49,300 --> 00:18:54,740
And this lady... Well, she'll do well with errands.

264
00:18:54,740 --> 00:18:59,320
Ah, well. It's not a hard thing to do, but...

265
00:18:59,320 --> 00:19:04,450
Excuse me. If you're going to do that, can my family also...

266
00:19:04,450 --> 00:19:06,240
Family?

267
00:19:07,850 --> 00:19:11,270
Ah, because I saved Young Master's life twice now,

268
00:19:11,270 --> 00:19:14,110
I couldn't look after my family.

269
00:19:15,300 --> 00:19:19,290
Hey, you also have family.

270
00:19:19,290 --> 00:19:21,380
At the Western district.

271
00:19:23,040 --> 00:19:26,410
Hyung-nim, she also has a family.

272
00:19:26,410 --> 00:19:32,610
They are all persevering. They will work hard for their food.

273
00:19:35,490 --> 00:19:38,900
Yes, hello. Yes, I'm part of the Ga Byeol Cho. Ga Byeol Cho!
(Ga Byeol Cho - living quarters)

274
00:19:44,200 --> 00:19:47,130
We're staying here?

275
00:19:47,130 --> 00:19:50,270
Hey, do you know how hard the training is here?

276
00:19:50,270 --> 00:19:52,010
You don't even know that you're widely opening the door to hardship.

277
00:19:52,010 --> 00:19:56,370
Hardship? That's something I always do. You said that food will be served on time?

278
00:19:56,370 --> 00:20:01,400
Wow. Seriously, Goryeo is really about connection, wealth, fame, and family!

279
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:03,940
Among those, connections are the best.

280
00:20:03,940 --> 00:20:08,010
How did you keep the family intact in the middle of that?

281
00:20:08,010 --> 00:20:10,750
It's my grandmother's method of discipline.

282
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:15,320
Then, I will be back.

283
00:20:20,980 --> 00:20:25,110
Thank you. For taking care of my village people.

284
00:20:26,130 --> 00:20:29,870
It's just me returning the favor for you keeping my secret.

285
00:20:35,530 --> 00:20:37,400
Let's go.

286
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:38,420
Where?

287
00:20:38,780 --> 00:20:40,550
Where are we going?

288
00:20:41,550 --> 00:20:43,350
Pick one.

289
00:20:46,550 --> 00:20:51,150
Look here. Please choose a pair for her to wear.

290
00:20:51,150 --> 00:20:55,160
If you brought your girlfriend here, the man should be choosing for her.

291
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:56,430
Is that so?

292
00:20:56,430 --> 00:21:00,440
You choose and then put it on her, that's how you do it.

293
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:03,650
We're not in that kind of relationship to pick out shoes

294
00:21:12,510 --> 00:21:14,090
Try them on.

295
00:21:28,470 --> 00:21:30,910
Does it fit or not?

296
00:21:30,910 --> 00:21:34,000
Well, I'm not sure.

297
00:21:42,860 --> 00:21:44,370
Give it here.

298
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:49,830
Is this a bit small?

299
00:22:06,750 --> 00:22:08,800
Just because I was being nice to you!

300
00:22:08,800 --> 00:22:10,080
It's strange!

301
00:22:11,910 --> 00:22:13,810
It feels ticklish.

302
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:23,540
Is that a woman or a thug?

303
00:22:28,810 --> 00:22:35,980
♫ Even during the times when I abandon myself ♫

304
00:22:35,980 --> 00:22:40,610
♫ you are on my side ♫

305
00:22:42,140 --> 00:22:43,920
It's strange... it's strange...

306
00:22:43,920 --> 00:22:49,300
♫ I recognized you a few times
Thanks to you, I am alive ♫

307
00:22:49,300 --> 00:22:56,500
♫ I restlessly follow your voice ♫

308
00:22:56,500 --> 00:22:58,670
♫ Even if for a thousand times ♫

309
00:22:58,670 --> 00:23:00,300
Do you like them?
♫ I pushed you down ♫

310
00:23:01,050 --> 00:23:02,390
You like them?
♫ I get captivated ♫

311
00:23:03,530 --> 00:23:09,250
♫ In your eyes, I am shining ♫

312
00:23:09,250 --> 00:23:11,670
Where did Ajussi say he would be?

313
00:23:11,670 --> 00:23:14,450
Didn't Hong In Bang release him from the Gyeong Wi Jong Pyeon?
(Gyeong Wi Jong Pyeon: order that prevents an exile from going into Gaegyeong after release)

314
00:23:14,450 --> 00:23:16,720
What are you going to do when you meet Teacher Sam Bong?

315
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:18,590
I can't believe what your telling me.

316
00:23:18,590 --> 00:23:21,870
How can you guarantee that General Lee Seong Gye will not withdraw the An Byeon Chaek?

317
00:23:21,870 --> 00:23:24,880
So I have to hurry and report this to Ajussi.

318
00:23:25,740 --> 00:23:28,150
I'm going to meet him first and tell him.

319
00:23:28,150 --> 00:23:31,650
For something like this, the one who caused the problem has to say it.

320
00:23:31,650 --> 00:23:33,290
That's your problem.

321
00:23:33,290 --> 00:23:35,100
Hey...

322
00:23:35,100 --> 00:23:39,070
To be honest I haven't met Sam Bong Teacher even once.

323
00:23:39,070 --> 00:23:41,840
But this time, we made the plan succeed together.

324
00:23:41,840 --> 00:23:45,750
This time I'm going to meet him and get scolded if he wants to scold me or complimented if he wants to compliment me

325
00:23:45,750 --> 00:23:48,970
That's why the person he needs to discuss the next step with

326
00:23:48,970 --> 00:23:51,070
is not you, but me.

327
00:23:51,070 --> 00:23:53,310
I also have my duty as a member.

328
00:23:53,310 --> 00:23:54,800
I'm going to meet him first.

329
00:23:54,800 --> 00:23:56,640
You don't even know where he is.

330
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:58,690
You, do you know something?

331
00:23:59,670 --> 00:24:03,170
He's coming back to Gaegyeong after eight years.

332
00:24:03,170 --> 00:24:05,810
I think I know where he would go.

333
00:24:25,960 --> 00:24:28,010
Because of the one word you said, I bet my life,

334
00:24:28,010 --> 00:24:30,700
but where are you?

335
00:24:36,510 --> 00:24:38,740
The letter is gone.

336
00:24:38,740 --> 00:24:43,190
Does that mean Sam Bong has finally come?

337
00:25:14,260 --> 00:25:17,600
New Jo Seon

338
00:25:18,120 --> 00:25:21,750
Finally! Finally we get to meet.

339
00:25:23,830 --> 00:25:25,790
Okay

340
00:25:25,790 --> 00:25:28,680
This is how men meet.

341
00:25:29,550 --> 00:25:33,180
A historical meeting is like this.

342
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:41,350
Ddang Sae: Lee Bang Ji in the future

343
00:25:41,350 --> 00:25:44,320
Just who is he?

344
00:25:44,320 --> 00:25:46,260
That idiot.

345
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:07,380
Who are you?

346
00:27:12,710 --> 00:27:17,690
I have waited for such a long time to meet you.

347
00:27:17,690 --> 00:27:19,280
Me?

348
00:27:19,280 --> 00:27:21,100
Yes.

349
00:27:21,100 --> 00:27:22,730
Teacher.

350
00:27:22,730 --> 00:27:26,060
A disciple I don't even know.

351
00:27:27,450 --> 00:27:31,370
Then is the man behind me waiting to meet me as well?

352
00:27:31,370 --> 00:27:32,970
What?

353
00:27:44,700 --> 00:27:47,210
I've waited a long time.

354
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:49,960
Sam Bong.

355
00:27:54,330 --> 00:27:57,190
You. You are...

356
00:27:59,030 --> 00:28:01,180
You came as well!

357
00:28:01,180 --> 00:28:03,210
Do you

358
00:28:03,210 --> 00:28:04,620
know me?

359
00:28:04,620 --> 00:28:06,310
Of course I do.

360
00:28:06,310 --> 00:28:08,500
I know you very well

361
00:28:08,500 --> 00:28:10,440
But I don't know you.

362
00:28:11,130 --> 00:28:12,320
Who are you?

363
00:28:12,320 --> 00:28:14,680
Well who are you?

364
00:28:14,680 --> 00:28:17,160
The one who had his life stripped away because of you.

365
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:19,400
I don't know you. I've never seen you,

366
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:21,770
yet I scammed you?

367
00:28:21,770 --> 00:28:23,690
Who are you?

368
00:28:29,070 --> 00:28:32,780
I know both of you.

369
00:28:32,780 --> 00:28:36,760
And very well at that.

370
00:28:36,760 --> 00:28:38,000
Who are you?

371
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:41,340
Right, who are you?

372
00:28:43,120 --> 00:28:44,710
I am

373
00:28:45,530 --> 00:28:48,680
Lee Bang Won.

374
00:28:48,680 --> 00:28:50,440
Lee Bang Won?

375
00:28:51,680 --> 00:28:55,110
But after listening to the two of you speaking,

376
00:28:55,110 --> 00:28:59,650
it appears that the swordsman didn't move according to your order.

377
00:29:04,700 --> 00:29:08,290
To think this great cause was put into motion by tangling with the inevitable, as well as a coincidence.

378
00:29:08,290 --> 00:29:13,450
This is like Heaven's "Un" and Land's "Myeong" meeting.
(Un: fortune, Myeong: order/God's will, Un Myeong: fate)

379
00:29:16,080 --> 00:29:20,710
In each battlefield, he comes like the wind and defeats Japanese pirates,

380
00:29:21,600 --> 00:29:23,430
The Viper.

381
00:29:23,430 --> 00:29:25,470
How do you know?

382
00:29:26,310 --> 00:29:28,100
The Viper?

383
00:29:28,100 --> 00:29:32,780
I followed the Viper and found this cave.

384
00:29:33,540 --> 00:29:35,900
I came to know your will.

385
00:29:35,900 --> 00:29:38,200
You followed me?

386
00:29:39,910 --> 00:29:44,650
The day that you killed Dae Sa Seong Baek Yoon,

387
00:29:47,530 --> 00:29:49,890
I was there.

388
00:29:51,900 --> 00:29:53,460
Also,

389
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:58,220
this letter.

390
00:30:02,280 --> 00:30:06,940
I saw this and to find the owner of this room.

391
00:30:06,940 --> 00:30:09,360
I went out to find the Viper.

392
00:30:14,920 --> 00:30:17,290
Pyeong Jeong Ji Gye.
(Pyeong Jeong Ji Gye: a plan to make a fair and righteous world)

393
00:30:17,290 --> 00:30:19,570
Pyeong Jeong Ji Gye?

394
00:30:19,570 --> 00:30:21,430
How did you know about the Pyeong Jeong Ji Gye?

395
00:30:21,430 --> 00:30:24,780
Does it matter how I knew about it?

396
00:30:25,760 --> 00:30:28,360
The only important thing is,

397
00:30:29,560 --> 00:30:34,350
I followed your plan but this country has become more chaotic.

398
00:30:34,350 --> 00:30:37,550
This rotten Goryeo is far from ending.

399
00:30:38,550 --> 00:30:41,530
It is getting more rotten and is collapsing.

400
00:30:42,660 --> 00:30:44,560
Your plan

401
00:30:46,070 --> 00:30:47,540
was wrong.

402
00:30:47,540 --> 00:30:49,020
No.

403
00:30:50,030 --> 00:30:51,910
I might not know what the Pyeong Jeong Ji Gye is,

404
00:30:51,910 --> 00:30:55,270
but if it's a plan to smash this rotten Goryeo,

405
00:30:56,300 --> 00:30:59,080
that is going well.

406
00:31:01,890 --> 00:31:05,990
The day that you killed Baek Yoon, it was started.

407
00:31:07,430 --> 00:31:09,560
And yesterday,

408
00:31:09,560 --> 00:31:13,840
because of your attack on Hong In Bang, the An Byeon Chaek got approved.

409
00:31:17,140 --> 00:31:20,020
The three of us created this situation.

410
00:31:20,790 --> 00:31:23,250
Now Goryeo will

411
00:31:23,250 --> 00:31:25,740
begin a new era.

412
00:31:27,830 --> 00:31:30,140
New era?

413
00:31:31,780 --> 00:31:34,400
What's a new era?

414
00:31:35,230 --> 00:31:39,070
Faultless people who cultivated a wasteland getting killed?

415
00:31:39,070 --> 00:31:44,920
Or taking lands from the people with the excuse of protecting them from Japanese pirates?

416
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:46,670
That.

417
00:31:47,520 --> 00:31:51,420
is that the new era you are talking about?

418
00:31:51,420 --> 00:31:54,380
It's a process that we have to go through.

419
00:31:54,380 --> 00:31:58,130
For every great cause, hardship follows.

420
00:32:00,840 --> 00:32:02,460
Cause...

421
00:32:03,720 --> 00:32:05,490
Hardship...

422
00:32:07,610 --> 00:32:10,460
Teacher, what you said was right.

423
00:32:10,460 --> 00:32:13,560
You said that the thoughts of people in politics are of little value.

424
00:32:13,560 --> 00:32:18,070
Look at the big picture? Don't look at the tree but the whole forest?

425
00:32:20,020 --> 00:32:23,020
The wild grass that gets stepped on there

426
00:32:24,220 --> 00:32:26,520
doesn't even have peace.

427
00:32:30,090 --> 00:32:32,430
is it going well?

428
00:32:33,450 --> 00:32:35,370
In that process that's going well,

429
00:32:35,370 --> 00:32:38,210
how many people need to die?

430
00:32:38,210 --> 00:32:41,230
How many more need to die for that damn Pyeong Jeong Ji Gye

431
00:32:41,230 --> 00:32:44,070
to end Goryeo?

432
00:32:51,310 --> 00:32:53,030
But,

433
00:32:54,110 --> 00:32:56,140
"it's going well".

434
00:32:56,140 --> 00:32:58,790
I started it?

435
00:33:08,860 --> 00:33:11,270
It was my fault.

436
00:33:11,270 --> 00:33:13,080
I

437
00:33:13,820 --> 00:33:17,280
