438
00:33:17,280 --> 00:33:19,850
Shouldn't you listen to my explanation as well?

439
00:33:19,850 --> 00:33:22,250
I was going to do that, but

440
00:33:22,250 --> 00:33:24,730
just now I realized,

441
00:33:25,750 --> 00:33:27,940
even if I listen to what you are going to say,

442
00:33:27,940 --> 00:33:30,940
there's no turning back.

443
00:33:30,940 --> 00:33:32,440
We

444
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:35,880
will not see each other again.

445
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:38,660
We will meet again.

446
00:33:42,030 --> 00:33:45,150
If I meet you again,

447
00:33:47,590 --> 00:33:50,230
I might kill you then.

448
00:34:27,270 --> 00:34:31,020
It's that person. The one who left a letter for Bon Won.

449
00:34:37,320 --> 00:34:39,390
He will come back.

450
00:34:41,180 --> 00:34:43,510
He trusted your plan and executed it.

451
00:34:43,510 --> 00:34:46,460
Don't you think he's someone who has a lot of rage against this Goryeo?

452
00:34:46,460 --> 00:34:48,370
Did you say you are Lee Bang Won?

453
00:34:48,370 --> 00:34:49,820
Yes.

454
00:34:50,520 --> 00:34:52,230
I,

455
00:34:53,470 --> 00:34:56,900
General Lee Seong Gye's fifth son,

456
00:34:56,900 --> 00:34:58,820
am Lee Bang Won.

457
00:35:05,480 --> 00:35:12,200
No difference. No difference.

458
00:35:12,200 --> 00:35:17,040
Ask the world...

459
00:35:18,190 --> 00:35:25,360
When deciding life and death, between politics

460
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:31,100
and a sword, what difference is there.

461
00:35:32,020 --> 00:35:37,930
♫ Nameless bird in the sky ♫

462
00:35:37,930 --> 00:35:45,550
♫ why do you cry you mournfully? ♫

463
00:35:45,550 --> 00:35:52,090
♫ The ground where the flower wilted ♫

464
00:35:52,090 --> 00:35:55,600
♫ can't be found anyway ♫

