466
00:35:59,690 --> 00:36:02,520
Don't smile! I'll fall for you.

467
00:36:03,330 --> 00:36:05,650
I'm hungry.

468
00:36:06,720 --> 00:36:08,380
Do you have rice?

469
00:36:09,020 --> 00:36:10,490
You should know shame.

470
00:36:10,490 --> 00:36:13,070
You're missing performances every day, so why are you talking about food?

471
00:36:13,070 --> 00:36:14,120
We don't have rice.

472
00:36:14,120 --> 00:36:15,620
Sorry.

473
00:36:15,620 --> 00:36:18,440
From tomorrow, I won't skip and I'll do everything.

474
00:36:19,420 --> 00:36:22,470
Give me some rice. I might die from hunger!

475
00:36:22,470 --> 00:36:24,150
Whatever.

476
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:26,360
Give me some rice. I said I might die from hunger!

477
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:27,930
Give me some rice!

478
00:36:27,930 --> 00:36:30,420
