485
00:36:42,940 --> 00:36:45,230
Aigoo.

486
00:36:46,430 --> 00:36:48,350
You...

487
00:36:49,280 --> 00:36:51,290
Ddang Sae, you...

488
00:36:51,290 --> 00:36:53,660
You were that warrior?

489
00:36:57,180 --> 00:36:59,570
You killed Baek Yoon,

